440
00:53:08,880 --> 00:53:10,980
[SPEAKER_01] neko to objasniti.

441
00:53:10,980 --> 00:53:11,719
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno,

442
00:53:11,719 --> 00:53:14,119
[SPEAKER_01] bio je nedavno nekakva,

443
00:53:14,119 --> 00:53:15,719
[SPEAKER_01] isto je bila po Instagramu,

444
00:53:15,719 --> 00:53:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] jedna influencerica je stavila video

445
00:53:18,619 --> 00:53:20,400
[SPEAKER_01] kako urla neko djete

446
00:53:20,400 --> 00:53:22,719
[SPEAKER_01] i kako to treba zabraniti u avionu.

447
00:53:22,719 --> 00:53:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo, mislim si,

448
00:53:23,539 --> 00:53:27,039
[SPEAKER_01] pa postoje hoteli za samo odrasle,

449
00:53:27,039 --> 00:53:29,380
[SPEAKER_01] pa vjerojatno postoje i nekakvi privatni avioni,

450
00:53:29,380 --> 00:53:30,360
[SPEAKER_01] pa se vozi lijepo,

451
00:53:30,360 --> 00:53:31,679
[SPEAKER_01] pa odredi ko će biti u njemu.

452
00:53:31,679 --> 00:53:32,980
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedna stvar.

453
00:53:32,980 --> 00:53:33,480
[SPEAKER_01] A druga,

454
00:53:33,480 --> 00:53:37,059
[SPEAKER_01] ona mene pitala kako sam mogla to staviti,

455
00:53:37,059 --> 00:53:38,599
[SPEAKER_01] jer kako ja znam po glasu,

456
00:53:38,599 --> 00:53:39,460
[SPEAKER_01] znam ženo,

457
00:53:39,460 --> 00:53:41,260
[SPEAKER_01] onaj ko ima djete s poteškoćama,

458
00:53:41,260 --> 00:53:44,039
[SPEAKER_01] taj već po glasu zna prepoznat,

459
00:53:44,039 --> 00:53:46,739
[SPEAKER_01] to nešto u glasu.

460
00:53:46,739 --> 00:53:47,840
[SPEAKER_01] I moj Ivan ovako,

461
00:53:47,840 --> 00:53:48,980
[SPEAKER_01] kao odmah me krenu držati,

462
00:53:48,980 --> 00:53:49,380
[SPEAKER_01] stani to,

463
00:53:49,380 --> 00:53:50,619
[SPEAKER_01] nećeš nigdje hodati,

464
00:53:50,619 --> 00:53:51,659
[SPEAKER_01] prestani više non stop se.

465
00:53:51,659 --> 00:53:52,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ja rekao,

466
00:53:52,599 --> 00:53:53,019
[SPEAKER_01] ali Ivane,

467
00:53:53,019 --> 00:53:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] možda je djete tamo samo,

468
00:53:54,739 --> 00:53:56,019
[SPEAKER_01] možda sestra ne zna s njim,

469
00:53:56,019 --> 00:53:57,039
[SPEAKER_01] možda ću moći pomoći,

470
00:53:57,039 --> 00:53:58,239
[SPEAKER_01] možda mame nema.

471
00:53:58,239 --> 00:53:58,500
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš,

472
00:53:58,500 --> 00:54:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] čujem po glasu da je neka panika,

473
00:54:01,000 --> 00:54:03,920
[SPEAKER_01] a čujem da je...

474
00:54:03,920 --> 00:54:05,880
[SPEAKER_01] I ja na kraju nisam izdržala,

475
00:54:05,980 --> 00:54:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] odšla sam tamo hodnikom,

476
00:54:07,539 --> 00:54:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] jer smo čekali duže

477
00:54:08,619 --> 00:54:11,340
[SPEAKER_01] i ugledam zapravo da je to žena

478
00:54:11,340 --> 00:54:12,340
[SPEAKER_01] koja ja poznajem,

479
00:54:12,340 --> 00:54:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] a bila je sa svojim sinom,

480
00:54:14,579 --> 00:54:15,840
[SPEAKER_01] ali jednostavno je bila situacija

481
00:54:15,840 --> 00:54:16,719
[SPEAKER_01] da ono,

482
00:54:16,719 --> 00:54:18,940
[SPEAKER_01] on je bio izvan sebe

483
00:54:18,940 --> 00:54:20,280
[SPEAKER_01] i zato je vikao,

484
00:54:20,280 --> 00:54:21,480
[SPEAKER_01] nije ga uspjevala,

485
00:54:22,059 --> 00:54:23,380
[SPEAKER_01] do kraja tamo ga malo umiri

486
00:54:23,380 --> 00:54:24,760
[SPEAKER_01] i on ponovno krene i tako,

487
00:54:24,760 --> 00:54:25,260
[SPEAKER_01] tako da,

488
00:54:25,260 --> 00:54:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] to možeš čuti više taj,

489
00:54:28,880 --> 00:54:32,219
[SPEAKER_01] razviješ taj sens za to,

490
00:54:32,219 --> 00:54:33,360
[SPEAKER_01] previše,

491
00:54:33,360 --> 00:54:34,719
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam od čega smo sad bili krenuli,

492
00:54:34,719 --> 00:54:35,599
[SPEAKER_01] pa sam završila od toga.

493
00:54:35,599 --> 00:54:36,800
[SPEAKER_01] Nije nebitno,

494
00:54:36,800 --> 00:54:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] ja razmišljam o tome kako,

495
00:54:38,340 --> 00:54:39,699
[SPEAKER_00] razmišljam kako ono,

496
00:54:39,699 --> 00:54:40,820
[SPEAKER_00] kad si roditelj,

497
00:54:40,820 --> 00:54:41,699
[SPEAKER_00] pa ti isto ono,

498
00:54:41,699 --> 00:54:42,840
[SPEAKER_00] poplaču već lagano,

499
00:54:42,840 --> 00:54:43,260
[SPEAKER_00] znaš,

500
00:54:43,260 --> 00:54:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] jer je li djete gladno,

501
00:54:44,360 --> 00:54:45,260
[SPEAKER_00] od toga smo krenuli, da.

502
00:54:45,260 --> 00:54:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] nervozno,

503
00:54:45,920 --> 00:54:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] a isto sam htjela dodat,

504
00:54:48,500 --> 00:54:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] apropo komentara,

505
00:54:51,019 --> 00:54:52,199
[SPEAKER_00] prije koji neko ima djecu,

506
00:54:52,199 --> 00:54:53,199
[SPEAKER_00] meni je najbolje kad sam čula,

507
00:54:53,199 --> 00:54:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] naj, kako je bilo,

508
00:54:55,000 --> 00:54:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] najlakše je odgojiti imaginarnu djecu.

509
00:54:58,380 --> 00:54:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

510
00:54:59,019 --> 00:55:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] O, ta djeca su perfektno odgojena,

511
00:55:01,039 --> 00:55:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer sve ide po pesu,

512
00:55:02,380 --> 00:55:03,579
[SPEAKER_00] sve si najpametniji.

513
00:55:03,579 --> 00:55:04,139
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je savršeno.

514
00:55:04,139 --> 00:55:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko od toga sam ja imala,

515
00:55:05,539 --> 00:55:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] jo, moja djeca neće se igrati sa puškama.

516
00:55:08,039 --> 00:55:09,679
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

517
00:55:09,679 --> 00:55:10,440
[SPEAKER_01] To sad.

518
00:55:10,440 --> 00:55:12,219
[SPEAKER_01] A ja sam ih znala i bacati,

519
00:55:12,219 --> 00:55:13,380
[SPEAKER_01] da budem iskana kao,

520
00:55:13,380 --> 00:55:15,139
[SPEAKER_01] dobiju na poklone ovo,

521
00:55:15,260 --> 00:55:17,579
[SPEAKER_01] onda skužiš da im je fora.

522
00:55:17,579 --> 00:55:18,940
[SPEAKER_01] Šta da ja sad radim?

523
00:55:18,940 --> 00:55:20,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ako se svi igraju s time,

524
00:55:20,119 --> 00:55:21,659
[SPEAKER_01] pa ne mogu ja sad njima reći.

525
00:55:21,659 --> 00:55:24,500
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, nećeš im dat nožove da se igra

526
00:55:24,500 --> 00:55:25,500
[SPEAKER_01] ako se svi igraju s time,

527
00:55:25,500 --> 00:55:27,340
[SPEAKER_01] ali opet, nekako, nekako,

528
00:55:27,340 --> 00:55:28,139
[SPEAKER_01] kao balans.

529
00:55:28,139 --> 00:55:29,400
[SPEAKER_01] Šta ja znam, ne znam.

530
00:55:29,400 --> 00:55:30,500
[SPEAKER_00] Barem imaš neka,

531
00:55:30,500 --> 00:55:32,139
[SPEAKER_00] mi, naše pravilo kućno,

532
00:55:32,139 --> 00:55:33,300
[SPEAKER_00] i onda, barem,

533
00:55:33,300 --> 00:55:35,179
[SPEAKER_00] kao prvo oni to zovu pucalica.

534
00:55:35,179 --> 00:55:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, ajde, nekako slađe samo po sebi.

535
00:55:39,000 --> 00:55:39,739
[SPEAKER_00] I rekli smo kao,

536
00:55:39,739 --> 00:55:41,320
[SPEAKER_00] nema jedan u drugog braća,

537
00:55:41,320 --> 00:55:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] nego u kauč, u zid,

538
00:55:43,659 --> 00:55:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] ako ima one mekane metke,

539
00:55:45,400 --> 00:55:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] i ako nema kao,

540
00:55:46,579 --> 00:55:47,219
[SPEAKER_00] ako nema isto,

541
00:55:47,219 --> 00:55:48,360
[SPEAKER_00] to mi ružno zavidjeti uopće.

542
00:55:48,360 --> 00:55:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ali dobro, kažem,

543
00:55:49,559 --> 00:55:51,659
[SPEAKER_00] svi mi imamo neka svoja čuvrsta pravila,

544
00:55:51,659 --> 00:55:53,420
[SPEAKER_00] onda dođu djeca i ne možeš sve.

545
00:55:53,420 --> 00:55:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno, biraš bitke uopće,

546
00:55:55,039 --> 00:55:57,099
[SPEAKER_00] šta je bitno, šta je nebitno.

547
00:55:57,099 --> 00:56:02,099
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko, pa ti brak,

548
00:56:02,099 --> 00:56:05,320
[SPEAKER_00] već si spomenula da bude često pucanje brakova

549
00:56:05,320 --> 00:56:07,840
[SPEAKER_00] u tim situacijama gdje se rodi djete,

550
00:56:07,840 --> 00:56:11,260
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno gdje diagnoza se postavi

551
00:56:11,260 --> 00:56:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] u nekom trenutku.

552
00:56:12,380 --> 00:56:16,280
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je kod vas bila situacija?

553
00:56:16,280 --> 00:56:17,699
[SPEAKER_00] Je li bilo kriza?

554
00:56:17,699 --> 00:56:19,179
[SPEAKER_00] Misli, svaki brak ima krize,

555
00:56:19,179 --> 00:56:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] ali kako izgledaju krize?

556
00:56:20,860 --> 00:56:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] U krizu je jutro.

557
00:56:21,980 --> 00:56:24,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ali da.

558
00:56:24,639 --> 00:56:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] Budu te mini krize.

559
00:56:27,039 --> 00:56:28,380
[SPEAKER_00] Moram se odreći.

560
00:56:28,380 --> 00:56:30,820
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ja svaki put kad se spremamo za misu,

561
00:56:30,820 --> 00:56:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] ja uvijek pomislim,

562
00:56:32,059 --> 00:56:34,400
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ne stave prva stvar da bude

563
00:56:34,400 --> 00:56:35,619
[SPEAKER_00] na misi mir s tobom?

564
00:56:35,840 --> 00:56:39,099
[SPEAKER_00] To bi prvo trebalo biti da s tim uđemo uopće,

565
00:56:39,099 --> 00:56:41,780
[SPEAKER_00] jer spremanje je vjerojatno eskaliralo u jednom trenutku.

566
00:56:41,780 --> 00:56:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ali one neke malo konkretnije krize.

567
00:56:45,340 --> 00:56:46,159
[SPEAKER_00] Kako?

568
00:56:46,159 --> 00:56:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] Je li ono, sjedneš, dogovoriš se,

569
00:56:48,019 --> 00:56:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] gle, ono, ajmo to probati izvjeći ili upadneš?

570
00:56:50,619 --> 00:56:51,039
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je jako teško.

571
00:56:51,039 --> 00:56:52,260
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je stvarno teško to,

572
00:56:52,260 --> 00:56:53,380
[SPEAKER_01] pogotovo taj period,

573
00:56:53,380 --> 00:56:56,019
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam zapravo ja nas ugurala,

574
00:56:56,019 --> 00:56:57,239
[SPEAKER_01] taj kao, ajmo prodati stan,

575
00:56:57,239 --> 00:56:58,980
[SPEAKER_01] kupiti kuću da on može imati dvorište,

576
00:56:58,980 --> 00:57:00,539
[SPEAKER_01] trampolin, ljulju, znaš.

577
00:57:00,539 --> 00:57:01,139
[SPEAKER_01] A mužak,

578
00:57:01,139 --> 00:57:03,199
[SPEAKER_01] tamo smo završili stan,

579
00:57:03,199 --> 00:57:04,179
[SPEAKER_01] a on je dosta onako,

580
00:57:04,179 --> 00:57:05,699
[SPEAKER_01] on ne može,

581
00:57:05,699 --> 00:57:06,920
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, ne može niko,

582
00:57:06,920 --> 00:57:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] niko ne voli taj stres i pressing

583
00:57:08,539 --> 00:57:10,400
[SPEAKER_01] i neizvjesnost.

584
00:57:10,400 --> 00:57:12,320
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, ono, nikome to nije super.

585
00:57:12,320 --> 00:57:13,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ali on baš to, onako,

586
00:57:13,679 --> 00:57:16,099
[SPEAKER_01] izbjegava u širokom luku koliko može.

587
00:57:16,099 --> 00:57:18,199
[SPEAKER_01] Kao sad smo tamo završili stan,

588
00:57:18,199 --> 00:57:20,159
[SPEAKER_01] kuć sad, šta ćemo sad prodavat?

589
00:57:20,159 --> 00:57:22,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ali znaš, ali njemu bi bilo super.

590
00:57:22,320 --> 00:57:23,780
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, baš sam tu vidjela baš te kuće.

591
00:57:23,780 --> 00:57:25,260
[SPEAKER_01] Di si ti vidjela sad?

592
00:57:25,260 --> 00:57:26,980
[SPEAKER_01] Di se prodaje kuće kao?

593
00:57:26,980 --> 00:57:29,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ja, mi smo doslovno iza zgrade,

594
00:57:29,400 --> 00:57:30,559
[SPEAKER_01] si kupili kuću,

595
00:57:30,559 --> 00:57:31,940
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj, prodali smo stan,

596
00:57:31,940 --> 00:57:32,940
[SPEAKER_01] kupili tu kuću

597
00:57:32,940 --> 00:57:33,980
[SPEAKER_01] i onda renovacija.

598
00:57:33,980 --> 00:57:35,139
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ti majstor.

599
00:57:35,139 --> 00:57:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, užas, užas.

600
00:57:37,420 --> 00:57:38,280
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je trajalo to?

601
00:57:38,280 --> 00:57:39,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ta agonija s majstorom?

602
00:57:39,400 --> 00:57:41,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ma, predugo.

603
00:57:41,300 --> 00:57:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sad smo već krenuli kao,

604
00:57:45,079 --> 00:57:47,360
[SPEAKER_01] ono, procurila je terasa u novu kuhinju,

605
00:57:47,360 --> 00:57:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] pa nam dolazi majstor

606
00:57:48,380 --> 00:57:49,719
[SPEAKER_01] koji nam je radio u stanu,

607
00:57:49,719 --> 00:57:51,119
[SPEAKER_01] u kojeg imamo povjerenje,

608
00:57:51,300 --> 00:57:53,280
[SPEAKER_01] ali kojeg nismo uzeli samo iz razloga,

609
00:57:53,280 --> 00:57:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] jer dok su završili svi ti krediti,

610
00:57:54,960 --> 00:57:56,679
[SPEAKER_01] obrade, sve kad smo ga kontaktirali,

611
00:57:56,679 --> 00:57:58,440
[SPEAKER_01] trebali smo ga čekati šest mjeseci.

612
00:57:58,440 --> 00:58:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] I kao, ajbal, mi bi da neko odmah krene,

613
00:58:01,960 --> 00:58:03,360
[SPEAKER_01] kao, kaj ćemo tu kuću,

614
00:58:03,360 --> 00:58:04,079
[SPEAKER_01] kako ćemo?

615
00:58:04,079 --> 00:58:04,820
[SPEAKER_01] I na kraju,

616
00:58:04,820 --> 00:58:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] ti s kojima smo radili su,

617
00:58:07,539 --> 00:58:09,219
[SPEAKER_01] na kraju, ono, isto krenuli,

618
00:58:09,219 --> 00:58:10,820
[SPEAKER_01] pa korona, pa ovo,

619
00:58:10,820 --> 00:58:12,139
[SPEAKER_01] sto su imali izlika.

620
00:58:13,599 --> 00:58:16,480
[SPEAKER_01] na kraju trebali još sedam puta duže,

621
00:58:16,480 --> 00:58:18,860
[SPEAKER_01] nego što bi ovaj da je krenuo za šest mjeseci,

622
00:58:18,860 --> 00:58:20,420
[SPEAKER_01] jer je on fakat, ono,

623
00:58:20,420 --> 00:58:23,480
[SPEAKER_01] čovjek je naučio zanatu svog brata u Njemačkoj,

624
00:58:23,480 --> 00:58:25,099
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno je pravi, ono,

625
00:58:25,099 --> 00:58:26,719
[SPEAKER_01] posloženi jedan čovjek,

626
00:58:26,719 --> 00:58:28,239
[SPEAKER_01] rijetkost od majstora,

627
00:58:28,239 --> 00:58:30,980
[SPEAKER_01] ali mi je rekao da ga ne smijem više nikom preporučiti.

628
00:58:31,320 --> 00:58:33,679
[SPEAKER_01] Da ćeš mi broj, ali vjerojatno nećeš.

629
00:58:33,679 --> 00:58:36,420
[SPEAKER_01] Da, je iza sebe stan obrisao mopom,

630
00:58:36,420 --> 00:58:39,519
[SPEAKER_01] znači ja, čovjek je pola stana razbio, pregradio,

631
00:58:39,519 --> 00:58:41,639
[SPEAKER_01] radio sve pločice instalacije,

632
00:58:41,639 --> 00:58:43,659
[SPEAKER_01] novi parket u jednoj sobi,

633
00:58:43,659 --> 00:58:45,380
[SPEAKER_01] sve živo, onako,

634
00:58:45,380 --> 00:58:48,019
[SPEAKER_01] iza sebe mopom obrisao čovjek.

635
00:58:48,019 --> 00:58:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] I,

636
00:58:48,960 --> 00:58:51,579
[SPEAKER_01] i rekla sam, takve se čeka,

637
00:58:51,579 --> 00:58:54,860
[SPEAKER_01] više nikad Marija u našoj kući što god se bude raditi,

638
00:58:54,860 --> 00:58:56,460
[SPEAKER_01] ja tebe zovem ne zanima me,

639
00:58:56,460 --> 00:58:59,280
[SPEAKER_01] i sad nam je on našao isto čovjeka koji je morao popravljati krov,

640
00:58:59,280 --> 00:59:01,219
[SPEAKER_01] koji je tek napravljen, ali je prosurio.

641
00:59:01,320 --> 00:59:04,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ovaj,

